comments: Bjelica (SAC) makes contact with the ball and cleanly deflects Jokic's (DEN) pass attempt.

Hield (SAC) does not establish a legal guarding position in Murray's (DEN) path and he delivers body contact during the upward shooting motion on Murray's jump shot attempt. Replay review of the shooting foul called on Hield (SAC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Grant (DEN) places a hand on the opposite side of Holmes' (SAC) body while he's stationary during the pick but he immediately removes that hand. As Holmes moves away.
Bogdanovic (SAC) initiates contact to Grant's (DEN) body and arm as he receives the pass. The contact affects his FOM.
Bjelica (SAC) is in the paint for longer than 3 seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Bogdanovic (SAC) reaches back and briefly places a hand on the opposite side of Grant's (DEN) body during the rebound but he immediately removes his hand. The contact is deemed marginal.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Jokic (DEN) jumps vertically and his left arm collapses to his body as he absorbs the oncoming contact with Fox (SAC) during the driving shot attempt.

Murray (DEN) briefly grasps Holmes' (SAC) arm as both players establish rebounding position while the ball is on the rim. Murray immediately removes his hands as the ball rolls off of the rim. The contact is deemed marginal.
Jokic (DEN) briefly grasps Hield's (SAC) arm off ball while establishing position in the post but the marginal contact does not affect Hield's ability to defend.
Plumlee (DEN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bogdanovic (SAC) after the release of the ball that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (SAC) makes contact with the ball and cleanly deflects the inbound pass intended for  Murray (DEN).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the on-court ruling stands and DEN maintains possession of the ball.
Fox (SAC) reaches in and makes contact to Barton's (DEN) arm which affects his ability to pass.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Barnes (SAC) loses control of the ball during his drive and he is the last to touch it before the ball bounces out of bounds.
